<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='218:245'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-1a' );" name="012-1a" class="pb">[012-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='245:263'>監本纂圖重言重意互註尚書卷第十二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='263:278'>畢命第二十六　周書　孔氏傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='278:314'>康王命作冊畢<span class='krp-note'>命爲冊書/以命畢公</span>分居里成周郊<span class='krp-note'>分別民之/居里異其</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='314:354'><span class='krp-note'>善惡成定東周郊境/使有保護別彼列反</span>作畢命畢命<span class='krp-note'>言畢公見/命之書</span>惟十有二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='354:397'>年六月庚午朏<span class='krp-note'>康王即位十二年六月三日庚午/朏普忽反徐芳尾反又芳憒反</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>六/月</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='397:427'><span class='krp-note'>庚午朏召誥篇/三月惟丙午朏</span>越三日壬申王朝歩自宗周至于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='427:478'>豐<span class='krp-note'>於朏三日壬申王朝行自宗周至于豐宗/周鎬京豐文王所都朝陟遥反鎬戸老反</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>王朝歩自/宗周至于</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='478:513'><span class='krp-note'>豐三武成召誥本/篇他篇無宗字</span>以成周之衆命畢公保釐東郊<span class='krp-note'>用/成</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='513:562'><span class='krp-note'>周之民衆命畢公使安理治正成周東郊令得所釐力/之反治正上直吏反一本作治政則依字讀令力呈反</span>王若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='562:582'>曰嗚呼父師惟文王武王敷大德于天下用克</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='582:609'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-1b' );" name="012-1b" class="pb">[012-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='609:657'>受殷命<span class='krp-note'>王順其事歎告畢公代周公爲大師爲東伯命之代/君陳言文武布大德於天下故天佑之用能受殷之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='657:693'><span class='krp-note'>王命大/師音泰</span>惟周公左右先王綏定厥家<span class='krp-note'>言周公助先/王安定其家</span>毖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='693:721'>殷頑民遷于洛邑密邇王室式化厥訓<span class='krp-note'>毖殷頑民/恐其叛亂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='721:759'><span class='krp-note'>故徙於洛邑密近王室用化其/教毖音袐近如字又附近之近</span>旣歷三紀丗變風移四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='759:800'>方無虞予一人以寜<span class='krp-note'>言殷民遷周巳經三紀丗代民易頑/者漸化四方無可度之事我天子用</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='800:847'><span class='krp-note'>安矣十二年曰紀父子曰/丗度待洛反舊作待路反</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>予一人以寜康誥/則予一人以懌</span>道有升降</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='847:880'>政由俗革不臧厥臧民罔攸觀<span class='krp-note'>天道有上下交接之/義政教有用俗改更</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='880:927'><span class='krp-note'>之理民之俗善以善養之俗有不善以法御之若/乃不善其善則民無所勸慕上時掌反更古行反</span>惟公懋德</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='927:951'>克勤小物弼亮四丗正色率下罔不祗師言<span class='krp-note'>言/公</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='951:994'><span class='krp-note'>勉行德能勤小物輔佐文武成康四丗爲公/卿正色率下下人無不敬仰師法懋音茂</span>嘉績多于先</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='994:1021'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-2a' );" name="012-2a" class="pb">[012-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='1021:1062'>王予小子垂拱仰成<span class='krp-note'>公之善功多大先人之美我小子爲/王垂拱仰公成理言其上顯父兄下</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='1062:1117'><span class='krp-note'>施子孫拱九勇反/仰如字徐五亮反</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>予小子六泰誓武成/金縢洛誥君陳本篇</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>垂拱仰成武/成垂拱而天</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='1117:1141'><span class='krp-note'>下/治</span>王曰嗚呼父師今予祗命公以周公之事往</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='1141:1183'>哉<span class='krp-note'>今我敬命公以周公所爲之事往爲之哉/言非周公所爲不敢枉公往治治直吏反</span>旌别淑慝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='1183:1216'>表厥宅里彰善癉惡樹之風聲<span class='krp-note'>言當識别頑民之善/惡表異其居里明其</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='1216:1253'><span class='krp-note'>爲善病其爲惡立其善風揚/其善聲别彼列反癉丁但反</span>弗率訓典殊厥井疆俾克</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='1253:1302'>畏慕<span class='krp-note'>其不循教道之常則殊其井居田界使能畏爲惡之禍/慕爲善之福所以沮勸俾必爾反沮辭汝反又慈吕反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='1302:1335'>申畫郊圻愼固封守以康四海<span class='krp-note'>郊圻雖舊所規畫當/重分明之又當謹愼</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='1335:1375'><span class='krp-note'>堅固封疆之守備以安四海京圻安/則四海安矣守徐始救反重直用反</span>政貴有恒辭尚體</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='1375:1416'>要不惟好異<span class='krp-note'>政以仁義爲常辭以理實爲要故貴尚/之若異於先王君子所不好好呼報反</span>商</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='1416:1443'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-2b' );" name="012-2b" class="pb">[012-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='1443:1471'>俗靡靡利口惟賢餘風未殄公其念哉<span class='krp-note'>紂以靡靡/利口惟賢</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='1471:1525'><span class='krp-note'>覆亡國家今殷民利口餘風/未絶公其念絶之覆芳服反</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>公其念哉益稷帝其念哉大/禹謨帝念哉益稷伊訓念哉</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1525:1545'>我聞曰丗禄之家鮮克由禮以蕩陵德實悖天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1545:1593'>道<span class='krp-note'>特言我聞自古有之丗有禄位而無禮教少不以放/蕩陵邈有德者如此實亂天道鮮息淺反悖布内反</span>重言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1593:1634'><span class='krp-note'>我聞曰六無逸二康誥/多士君陳本篇各一</span>敝化奢麗萬丗同流<span class='krp-note'>言敝俗相/化車服奢</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1634:1666'><span class='krp-note'>麗雖相去萬丗若/同一流敝歩寐反</span>兹殷庶士席寵惟舊怙侈滅義服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1666:1708'>美于人<span class='krp-note'>此殷衆士居寵日乆怙恃奢侈以滅德/義服飾過制美於其民言僭上怙音戸</span>驕淫矜侉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1708:1741'>將由惡終雖收放心閑之惟艱<span class='krp-note'>言殷衆士驕恣過制/矜其所能以自侉大</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1741:1790'><span class='krp-note'>如此不變將用惡自終雖今順從周制心未壓服以禮閑/禦其心惟艱侉苦瓜反壓於葉反又於甲反又於豔反</span>資</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1790:1810'>冨能訓惟以永年惟德惟義時乃大訓不由古</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1810:1837'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-3a' );" name="012-3a" class="pb">[012-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1837:1881'>訓于何其訓<span class='krp-note'>以冨資而能順義則惟可以長年命矣惟有/德義是乃大順若不用古訓典籍於何其能</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1881:1905'><span class='krp-note'>順/乎</span>王曰嗚呼父師邦之安危惟兹殷士不剛不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1905:1948'>柔厥德允修<span class='krp-note'>言邦國所以安危惟在和此殷士而巳治/之不剛不柔寛猛相濟則其德政信修立</span>惟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1948:1968'>周公克愼厥始惟君陳克和厥中惟公克成厥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1968:2013'>終<span class='krp-note'>周公遷殷頑民以消亂階能愼其始君陳弘周/公之訓能和其中畢公闡二公之烈能成其終</span>三后協</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='2013:2043'>心同厎于道道洽政治澤潤生民<span class='krp-note'>三君合心爲一/終始相成同致</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='2043:2097'><span class='krp-note'>于道道至普洽政化治理其德澤惠施乃浸潤生民言/三君之功不可不尚政治直吏反施始豉反浸子鴆反</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>道/洽</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='2097:2130'><span class='krp-note'>政治澤潤生民舜典/好生之德洽于民心</span>四夷左衽罔不咸頼予小子永</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='2130:2179'>膺多福<span class='krp-note'>言東夷西戎南蠻北狄𬒳髪左祍之人無不皆恃頼/三君之德我小子亦長受其多福祍而甚反又而鴆</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='2179:2228'><span class='krp-note'>反</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>予小子六泰誓武成/金縢洛誥君陳本篇</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>予小子永膺多福君陳/惟予一人膺受多福</span>公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='2228:2255'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-3b' );" name="012-3b" class="pb">[012-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='2255:2280'>其惟時成周建無窮之基亦有無窮之聞<span class='krp-note'>公其/惟以</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='2280:2322'><span class='krp-note'>是成周之治爲周家立無窮之基業於/公亦有無窮之名聞於後丗爲于僞反</span>子孫訓其成式惟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='2322:2360'>乂<span class='krp-note'>言後丗子孫順公/之成法惟以治</span>嗚呼罔曰弗克惟旣厥心<span class='krp-note'>人之爲/政無曰</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='2360:2401'><span class='krp-note'>不能惟在盡/其心而巳</span>罔曰民寡惟愼厥事<span class='krp-note'>無曰人少不足治也/惟在愼其政事無敢</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='2401:2438'><span class='krp-note'>輕之少/詩照反</span>欽若先王成烈以休于前政<span class='krp-note'>敬順文武成業/以美於前人之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='2438:2449'><span class='krp-note'>政所以/勉畢公</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='2449:2464'>君牙第二十七　周書　孔氏傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='2464:2498'>穆王命君牙爲周大司徒<span class='krp-note'>穆王康王孫昭王子穆/王名滿君牙或作君雅</span>作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='2498:2536'>君牙<span class='krp-note'>君牙/臣名</span>君牙<span class='krp-note'>命以其名/遂以名篇</span>王若曰嗚呼君牙<span class='krp-note'>順其/事而</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='2536:2563'><span class='krp-note'>歎稱其名/而命之</span>惟乃祖乃父丗篤忠貞服勞王家厥有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='2563:2590'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-4a' );" name="012-4a" class="pb">[012-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='2590:2633'>成績紀于太常<span class='krp-note'>言汝父祖丗厚忠貞服事勤勞王家其有/成功見紀録書於王之太常以表顯之王</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='2633:2673'><span class='krp-note'>之旌旗畫日月曰/太常畫胡卦反</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>乃祖乃父五/餘見盤庚</span>惟予小子嗣守文武</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='2673:2700'>成康遺緒亦惟先王之臣克左右亂四方<span class='krp-note'>惟我小/子繼守</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='2700:2754'><span class='krp-note'>先王遺業亦惟父祖之臣能/佐助我治四方言己無所能</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>惟予小子二/又見泰誓</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>嗣守文武/成康遺緒</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='2754:2790'><span class='krp-note'>顧命嗣守/文武大訓</span>心之憂危若蹈虎尾渉于春冰<span class='krp-note'>言祖宗之/大已才之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='2790:2832'><span class='krp-note'>弱故心懷危懼虎尾畏噬春冰畏䧟危懼/之甚蹈徒報反噬市制反䧟䧟没之䧟</span>今命爾予翼作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='2832:2879'>股肱心膂<span class='krp-note'>今命汝爲我輔翼股肱心/膂之臣言委任膂音旅</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>作股肱心膂益稷/臣作朕股肱耳目</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='2879:2906'>纉乃舊服無忝祖考弘敷五典式和民則<span class='krp-note'>繼汝先/祖故所</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='2906:2959'><span class='krp-note'>服忠勤無辱累祖考之道大布五常之教/用和民令有法則累劣僞反令力呈反</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>纉乃舊服仲虺/之誥纉禹舊服</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='2959:2992'><span class='krp-note'>〇弘敷五典周官敷/五典舜典謹徽五典</span>爾身克正罔敢弗正民心罔中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='2992:3019'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-4b' );" name="012-4b" class="pb">[012-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='3019:3059'>惟爾之中<span class='krp-note'>言汝身能正則下無敢不正民心無/中從汝取中必當正身示民以中正</span>夏暑雨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='3059:3095'>小民惟曰怨咨<span class='krp-note'>夏月暑雨天之常道小人惟/曰怨歎咨嗟言心無中也</span>冬祁寒小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='3095:3139'>民亦惟曰怨咨<span class='krp-note'>冬大寒亦天之/常道民猶怨嗟</span>互註<span class='krp-note'>記緇衣君雅曰夏日/暑雨小民惟曰怨資</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='3139:3183'><span class='krp-note'>冬祁寒小民亦惟曰怨注云資當爲至齊魯/之語聲之誤也祁之言是也齊西偏之語也</span>厥惟艱哉思</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='3183:3221'>其艱以圖其易民乃寜<span class='krp-note'>天不可怨民猶怨嗟治民其惟/艱哉當思慮其難以謀其易民</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='3221:3261'><span class='krp-note'>乃安易/以豉反</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>厥惟艱哉伊訓兹惟/艱哉泰誓是惟艱哉</span>嗚呼丕顯哉文王謨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='3261:3297'><span class='krp-note'>歎文王所/謀大顯明</span>丕承哉武王烈<span class='krp-note'>言武王業美/大可承奉</span>啓佑我後人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='3297:3342'>咸以正罔缺<span class='krp-note'>文武之謀業大明可承奉開助我/後嗣皆以正道無邪缺缺苦穴反</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>啓佑/我後</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='3342:3377'><span class='krp-note'>人太甲啓/迪後人</span>爾惟敬明乃訓用奉若于先王<span class='krp-note'>汝惟當敬/明汝五教</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='3377:3413'><span class='krp-note'>用奉順于/先王之道</span>對揚文武之光命追配于前人<span class='krp-note'>言當荅揚/文武光明</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='3413:3440'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-5a' );" name="012-5a" class="pb">[012-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='3440:3484'><span class='krp-note'>之命君臣各追配/於前令名之人</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>對揚文武之光命顧命/用荅揚文武之光訓</span>王若曰君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='3484:3511'>牙乃惟由先正舊典時式民之治亂在兹<span class='krp-note'>汝惟當/奉用先</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='3511:3558'><span class='krp-note'>正之臣所行故事舊典文籍是法民之治亂在此/而巳用之則民治廢之則民亂治直吏反下注同</span>率乃祖考</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='3558:3594'>之攸行昭乃辟之有乂<span class='krp-note'>言當循汝父祖之所行明/汝君之有治功辟必亦反</span>重言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='3594:3614'><span class='krp-note'>率乃祖考之攸行太/甲率乃祖之攸行</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='3614:3629'>冏命第二十八　周書　孔氏傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='3629:3666'>穆王命伯冏爲周太僕正<span class='krp-note'>伯冏臣名也太僕長太御中/大夫冏九永反亦作煛長誅</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='3666:3697'><span class='krp-note'>丈/反</span>作冏命冏命<span class='krp-note'>以冏見/命名篇</span>王若曰伯冏惟予弗克于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='3697:3736'>德嗣先人宅丕后<span class='krp-note'>順其事以命伯冏言我不能於道/德繼先人居大君之位人輕任重</span>怵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='3736:3770'>惕惟厲中夜以興思免厥愆<span class='krp-note'>言常悚懼惟危夜半以/起思所以免其過悔怵</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='3770:3797'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-5b' );" name="012-5b" class="pb">[012-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='3797:3824'><span class='krp-note'>勑律反惕/他歷反</span>昔在文武聦明齊聖小大之臣咸懷忠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='3824:3875'>良<span class='krp-note'>聦明視聽逺齊通無滯礙臣雖/官有尊卑無不忠良礙五代反</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>昔在文武康王之誥/昔君文武〇聦明齊</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='3875:3915'><span class='krp-note'>聖堯典聦明文思微/子之命齊聖廣淵</span>其侍御僕從罔匪正人<span class='krp-note'>雖給侍進/御僕役從</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='3915:3956'><span class='krp-note'>官官雖微無不用中正之人御如字/一音禦從才用反注及下注侍從同</span>以旦夕承弼厥辟出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='3956:3994'>入起居罔有不欽<span class='krp-note'>小臣皆良僕役皆正以旦夕承輔/其君故君出入起居無有不敬</span>〇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='3994:4028'>重意<span class='krp-note'>罔有不欽盤庚下罔有/弗欽下文罔有不藏</span>發號施令罔有不臧下民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='4028:4071'>祗若萬邦咸休<span class='krp-note'>言文武發號施令無有不善下/民敬順其命萬國皆美其化</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>萬邦/咸休</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='4071:4102'><span class='krp-note'>二本篇洛誥大/禹謨萬邦咸寜</span>惟予一人無良實頼左右前後有位</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='4102:4143'>之士匡其不及<span class='krp-note'>惟我一人無善實恃左右前後有職位/之士匡正其不及言此責羣臣正己</span>〇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='4143:4181'>重意<span class='krp-note'>惟予一人無良泰誓惟予小子/無良君陳康王之誥惟予一人</span>繩愆糾謬格其非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='4181:4208'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-6a' );" name="012-6a" class="pb">[012-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='4208:4251'>心俾克紹先烈<span class='krp-note'>言侍左右之臣彈正過誤檢其非妄之心/使能繼先王之功業繩市陵反俾必爾反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='4251:4279'>今予命汝作大正正于羣僕侍御之臣<span class='krp-note'>欲其教正/羣僕無敢</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='4279:4321'><span class='krp-note'>佞/僞</span>懋乃后德交修不逮<span class='krp-note'>言侍御之臣無小大親踈皆當/勉汝君爲德更代修進其所不</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='4321:4347'><span class='krp-note'>及更古/衡反</span>愼簡乃僚無以巧言令色便辟側媚其惟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='4347:4396'>吉士<span class='krp-note'>當謹愼簡選汝僚屬侍臣無得用巧言無實令色無質/便辟足恭側媚謟䛕之人其惟皆吉良正士便婢綿反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='4396:4450'><span class='krp-note'>辟匹亦反徐扶亦反足/將住反䛕徐以朱反</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>無以巧言令色皐陶/謨何畏乎巧言令色</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>其惟吉/士二立</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='4450:4483'><span class='krp-note'>政本/篇</span>僕臣正厥后克正僕臣䛕厥后自聖<span class='krp-note'>言僕臣皆/正則其君</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='4483:4526'><span class='krp-note'>乃能正僕臣謟䛕/則其君乃自謂聖</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>僕臣䛕厥后自聖/說命良臣惟聖</span>后德惟臣不德</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='4526:4565'>惟臣<span class='krp-note'>君之有德惟臣成之君之無德惟/臣誤之言君所行善惡專在左右</span>爾無昵于憸人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='4565:4597'>充耳目之官迪上以非先王之典<span class='krp-note'>汝無親近於憸利/小子之人充備侍</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='4597:4624'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-6b' );" name="012-6b" class="pb">[012-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='4624:4680'><span class='krp-note'>從在視聽之官道君上以非先王之法昵女乙反憸息/廉反徐七漸反利口也本亦作<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2548' title='KR2548' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2548.png'/>近附近之近道音導</span>非人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='4680:4719'>其吉惟貨其吉<span class='krp-note'>若非人其實吉良惟以貨財配其吉/良以求入于僕侍之臣汝當清審</span>若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='4719:4765'>時<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1539' title='KR1539' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1539.png'/>厥官<span class='krp-note'>若用是行貨之人則/病其官職<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1539' title='KR1539' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1539.png'/>改頑反</span>惟爾大弗克祗厥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='4765:4804'>辟惟予汝辜<span class='krp-note'>用行貨之人則惟汝大不能敬其/君惟我則亦以此罪汝言不忠也</span>王曰嗚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='4804:4839'>呼欽哉永弼乃后于彞憲<span class='krp-note'>歎而勑之使敬用所言當/長輔汝君於常法此穆王</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='4839:4878'><span class='krp-note'>庶幾欲蹈/行常法</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>欽哉八堯典大禹謨微子之/命本篇各一舜典益稷各二</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='4878:4893'>吕刑第二十九　周書　孔氏傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='4893:4934'>吕命<span class='krp-note'>吕侯見命爲/天子司寇</span>穆王訓夏贖刑<span class='krp-note'>吕侯以穆王命作書/訓暢夏禹贖刑之法</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='4934:4974'><span class='krp-note'>更從輕以布告天/下贖音蜀注下同</span>作吕刑吕刑<span class='krp-note'>後爲甫侯故/或稱甫刑</span>惟吕命王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='4974:5017'>享國百年耄荒<span class='krp-note'>言吕侯見命爲卿時穆王以享國百年耄/亂荒忽穆王即位過四十矣言百年大期</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='5017:5044'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-7a' );" name="012-7a" class="pb">[012-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='5044:5089'><span class='krp-note'>雖老而能用賢以揚名耄本/亦作/毛報反切韻莫報反</span>度作刑以詰四方<span class='krp-note'>度時丗所/冝訓作贖</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='5089:5128'><span class='krp-note'>刑以治天下四方之民度待洛反/注同馬如字云法度也詰起一反</span>王曰若古有訓蚩尤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='5128:5166'>惟始作亂延及于平民<span class='krp-note'>順古有遺訓言蚩尤造始作亂/惡化相易延及於平善之人九</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='5166:5204'><span class='krp-note'>黎之君號曰蚩尤蚩尺之反尤有/牛反馬云少昊之末九黎君名</span>罔不寇賊鴟義姦宄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='5204:5249'>奪攘矯䖍<span class='krp-note'>平民化之無不相寇賊爲鴟䲷之義以相奪讓/矯稱上命若固有之亂之甚鴟尺之反鴟梟惡</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='5249:5286'><span class='krp-note'>鳥馬云鴟輕也義本亦作誼攘/如羊反矯居表反䖍其然反</span>苗民弗用靈制以刑惟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='5286:5328'>作五虐之刑曰法<span class='krp-note'>三苗之君習蚩尤之惡不用善化民而/制以重刑惟爲五虐之刑自謂得法蚩</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='5328:5381'><span class='krp-note'>尤黄帝所滅三苗帝堯/所誅言異丗而同惡</span>互註<span class='krp-note'>記緇衣君民者子以愛之則民親/之信以法之則民不倍恭以涖之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='5381:5426'><span class='krp-note'>則民有孫心甫刑曰苗民匪用命制以刑惟作/五虐之刑曰法是以民有惡德而遂絶其丗也</span>殺戮無辜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='5426:5465'>爰始淫爲劓刵椓黥<span class='krp-note'>三苗之主頑凶若民敢行虐刑以/殺戮無罪於是始大爲截人耳鼻</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='5465:5492'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-7b' );" name="012-7b" class="pb">[012-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='5492:5533'><span class='krp-note'>㭬隂黥面以加無辜故曰五虐劓魚器/反刵徐如志反椓丁角反黥其京反</span>越兹麗刑并制罔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='5533:5572'>差有辭<span class='krp-note'>苗民於此施刑并制無罪無差有直/辭者言淫濫麗力馳反并必政反</span>民興胥漸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='5572:5605'>泯泯棼棼罔中于信以覆詛盟<span class='krp-note'>三苗之民瀆於亂政/起相漸化泯泯爲亂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='5605:5658'><span class='krp-note'>棼棼同惡皆無中于信義以反背詛盟之約泯靣忍反徐音民/棼扶云反徐扶文反覆芳服反徐敷目反詛側助反背音佩約</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='5658:5685'><span class='krp-note'>如字又/於妙反</span>虐威庶戮方告無辜于上上帝監民罔有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='5685:5725'>馨香德刑發聞惟腥<span class='krp-note'>三苗虐政作威衆𬒳戮者方方各/告無罪於天天視苗民無有馨香</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='5725:5778'><span class='krp-note'>之行其所以爲德刑發聞惟乃腥臭聞/音問又如字注同腥音星行下孟反</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>罔有馨香德刑發/聞惟腥酒誥弗惟</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='5778:5812'><span class='krp-note'>德馨香祀登聞于天君/陳至治馨香感于神明</span>皇帝哀矜庶戮之不辜報虐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='5812:5850'>以威遏絶苗民無丗在下<span class='krp-note'>皇帝帝堯也哀矜衆𬒳戮者/之不辜乃報爲虐者以威誅</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='5850:5889'><span class='krp-note'>遏絶苗民使無丗位在下國也君/帝君冝作皇字帝堯也遏於葛反</span>乃命重黎絶地天通</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='5889:5916'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-8a' );" name="012-8a" class="pb">[012-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='5916:5963'>罔有降格<span class='krp-note'>重即羲黎即和堯命羲和丗掌天地四時之言使/人神不擾各得其序是謂絶地天通言天神無有</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='5963:6000'><span class='krp-note'>降地地祇不至於天明不相/干重直龍反注同黎力兮反</span>羣后之逮在下明明棐常</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='6000:6047'>鰥寡無蓋<span class='krp-note'>羣后諸侯之逮在下國皆以明明大道輔行常法/故使鰥寡得所無有掩蓋裴音匪又芳鬼反鰥居</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='6047:6081'><span class='krp-note'>頑/反</span>皇帝清問下民鰥寡有辭于苗<span class='krp-note'>帝堯詳問民患/皆有辭怨於苗</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='6081:6123'><span class='krp-note'>民清問馬/云清訊也</span>德威惟畏德明惟明<span class='krp-note'>言堯監苗民之見怨則/又増修其德行威則民</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='6123:6177'><span class='krp-note'>畏服明賢則德明/人所以無能名焉</span>互註<span class='krp-note'>記表記後丗雖有作者虞舜弗可及也/巳矣君天下生無私死不厚其子子民</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='6177:6230'><span class='krp-note'>如父母有憯怛之愛有忠利之教親而尊安而敬威而愛冨而/有禮惠而能散其君子尊仁畏義恥費輕實忠而不犯義而順</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='6230:6269'><span class='krp-note'>文而静寛而有辨甫刑曰德威惟威/德明惟明非虞帝其孰能如此乎</span>乃命三后恤功于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='6269:6289'>民伯夷降典折民惟刑禹平水土主名山川稷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='6289:6329'>降播種農殖嘉榖<span class='krp-note'>伯夷卜典禮教民而斷以法禹治洪/水山川無名者主名之后稷下教民</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='6329:6356'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-8b' );" name="012-8b" class="pb">[012-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='6356:6407'><span class='krp-note'>播種農畒生善榖所謂堯命三君憂功於民折之設反下同/馬鄭王皆音悊馬云智也種章用反殖承力反斷丁亂反</span>〇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='6407:6449'>重意<span class='krp-note'>禹平水土舜典咨禹汝平水土〇稷降/播種農殖嘉榖舜典汝后稷播時百榖</span>三后成功惟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='6449:6483'>殷于民<span class='krp-note'>各成其功惟所以殷盛/於民言禮教備衣食足</span>士制百姓于刑之中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='6483:6529'>以教祗德<span class='krp-note'>言伯夷道民典禮斷之以法皐陶作土制百官/於刑之中助成道化以教民爲敬德祇止而反</span>〇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='6529:6570'>重意<span class='krp-note'>士制百姓于刑之中大禹謨民恊于中/君陳惟厥中下文故乃明于刑之中</span>穆穆在上明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='6570:6600'>明在下灼于四方罔不惟德之勤<span class='krp-note'>堯躬行敬敬在/上三后之徒秉</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='6600:6652'><span class='krp-note'>明德明君道於下灼然彰著四/方故天下之士無不惟德之勤</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>灼于四方堯典光𬒳/四表泰誓光于四方</span>故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='6652:6685'>乃明于刑之中率乂于民棐彞<span class='krp-note'>天下皆勤立德故乃/能明於用刑之中正</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='6685:6725'><span class='krp-note'>循道以冶於民輔/成常教治直吏反</span>典獄非訖于威惟訖于冨<span class='krp-note'>言堯時主/獄有威有</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='6725:6766'><span class='krp-note'>德有恕非絶於威惟絶於富/丗治貨賂不行賂來故反</span>敬忌罔有擇言在身<span class='krp-note'>堯時/典獄</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='6766:6793'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-9a' );" name="012-9a" class="pb">[012-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='6793:6847'><span class='krp-note'>皆能敬其職忌其過故/無有可擇之言在其身</span>互註<span class='krp-note'>記表記子曰君子不失口於人是/故君子言足信也甫刑曰敬忌而</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='6847:6883'><span class='krp-note'>罔有擇/言在躬</span>惟克天德自作元命配享在下<span class='krp-note'>凡明於刑之/中無擇言在</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='6883:6918'><span class='krp-note'>身必是惟能天德自爲大/命配享天意在於天下</span>王曰嗟四方司政典獄非爾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='6918:6964'>惟作天牧<span class='krp-note'>主政典獄謂諸侯也非汝惟爲天牧民乎言任/重是汝爲于僞反任重上而鴆反下輕重之重</span>今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='6964:6994'>爾何監非時伯夷播刑之迪<span class='krp-note'>言當視是伯夷布/刑之道而法之</span>其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='6994:7023'>今爾何懲惟時苗民匪察于獄之麗<span class='krp-note'>其今汝何懲/戒乎所懲戒</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='7023:7057'><span class='krp-note'>惟是苗民非察於獄之施/刑以取滅亡麗力馳反</span>罔擇吉人觀于五刑之中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='7057:7100'>惟時庶威奪貨<span class='krp-note'>言苗民無肯選擇善人使觀視五刑之中/正惟是衆爲威虐者任之以奪取人貨所</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='7100:7129'><span class='krp-note'>以爲/亂</span>斷制五刑以亂無辜上帝不蠲降咎于苗<span class='krp-note'>苗/民</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='7129:7173'><span class='krp-note'>任奪貨姦人斷制五刑以亂加無罪天不㓗其/所爲故下咎罪謂誅之蠲吉縁反咎其九反</span>苗民無辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='7173:7200'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-9b' );" name="012-9b" class="pb">[012-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='7200:7235'>于罰乃絶厥丗<span class='krp-note'>言罪重無以辭於天罰故/堯絶其丗申言之爲至戒</span>王曰嗚呼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='7235:7273'>念之哉<span class='krp-note'>念以伯夷爲/法苗民爲戒</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>念之哉益稷/伊訓念哉</span>伯父伯兄仲叔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='7273:7302'>季弟㓜子童孫皆聽朕言庶有格命<span class='krp-note'>皆王同姓有/父兄弟子孫</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='7302:7353'><span class='krp-note'>列者伯仲叔季順少長也舉同姓包異姓言不殊也聽從/我言庶幾有至命聽如字又他經反少詩照反長丁丈反</span>重意</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='7353:7393'><span class='krp-note'>皆聽朕言湯誥悉聽朕言盤庚明聽/朕言泰誓咸聽朕言舜典咸聽朕命</span>今爾罔不由慰日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='7393:7433'>勤爾罔或戒不勤<span class='krp-note'>今汝無不用安自居日當勤之汝無/有徒念戒而不勤日勤上人實反一</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='7433:7467'><span class='krp-note'>音/曰</span>天齊于民俾我一日非終惟終在人<span class='krp-note'>天整齊於下/民使我爲之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='7467:7517'><span class='krp-note'>一日所行非爲天所終惟爲天所終在人所行天齊于民/絶句馬云齊中也俾我絶句上必爾反馬本作矜矜哀也</span>爾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='7517:7537'>尚敬逆天命以奉我一人雖畏勿畏雖休勿休</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='7537:7590'><span class='krp-note'>汝當庶幾敬逆天命以奉我一人之戒行事雖/見畏勿自謂可敬畏雖見美勿自謂有德羙</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>以奉我一/人泰誓奉</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='7590:7618'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-10a' );" name="012-10a" class="pb">[012-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='7618:7643'><span class='krp-note'>予一/人</span>惟敬五刑以成三德一人有慶兆民頼之其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='7643:7691'>寜惟永<span class='krp-note'>先戒以勞謙之德次教以惟敬五刑所以成剛柔正/直之三德也天予有善則兆民頼之其乃安寜長乆</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='7691:7746'><span class='krp-note'>之/道</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>一人有慶㤗誓/亦尚一人之慶</span>互註<span class='krp-note'>左襄十三年譲禮之主也范宣子/讓其下皆讓欒黶爲汰弗敢違也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='7746:7795'><span class='krp-note'>晉國以乎數丗頼之刑善也夫一人刑善百姓休和可不/務乎書曰一人有慶兆民頼之其寜惟永其是之謂乎</span>王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='7795:7829'>曰吁來有邦有土告爾祥刑<span class='krp-note'>吁歎也有國土諸侯告/汝以善用刑之道吁况</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='7829:7857'><span class='krp-note'>于反馬作/于于於也</span>在今爾安百姓何擇非人何敬非刑何</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='7857:7905'>度非及<span class='krp-note'>在今爾安百姓兆民之道當何所擇非惟吉人乎當/何所敬非惟五刑乎當何所度非惟及丗輕重所冝</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='7905:7947'><span class='krp-note'>乎度待洛反注/同馬云謀造也</span>兩造具備師聽五辭<span class='krp-note'>兩謂囚證造至也/兩至具備則衆獄</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='7947:7988'><span class='krp-note'>官共聽其入五刑之/辭造七報反注同</span>五辭簡孚正于五刑<span class='krp-note'>五辭簡核信/有罪驗則正</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='7988:8029'><span class='krp-note'>之於/五刑</span>五刑不簡正于五罰<span class='krp-note'>不簡核謂不應五刑當正/五罰出金贖罪核幸格反</span>五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='8029:8057'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-10b' );" name="012-10b" class="pb">[012-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='8057:8092'>罰不服正于五過<span class='krp-note'>不服不應罰也正於五過/從赦免應應對之應下同</span>五過之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='8092:8126'>疵惟官惟反惟内惟貨惟來<span class='krp-note'>五過之所病或甞同官/位或詐反囚辭或内親</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='8126:8168'><span class='krp-note'>用事或行貨枉法或舊相往來皆病所在/疵才斯反來馬本作求云有求請賕也</span>其罪惟鈞其審</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='8168:8216'>克之<span class='krp-note'>以病所在出入人罪使在五過罪與/犯法者同其當清察能使之不行</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>其克審之/四下文三</span>五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='8216:8244'>刑之疑有赦五罰之疑有赦其審克之<span class='krp-note'>刑疑赦從/罰罰疑赦</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='8244:8284'><span class='krp-note'>從免其當清/察能得其理</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>五罰之疑有赦/大禹罪疑惟輕</span>簡孚有衆惟貌有稽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='8284:8326'><span class='krp-note'>簡核誠信有合衆心惟察/其貌有所考合重刑之至</span>無簡不聽具嚴天威<span class='krp-note'>無簡核/誠信不</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='8326:8362'><span class='krp-note'>聽理其獄皆當嚴/敬天威無輕用刑</span>墨辟疑赦其罰百鍰閱實其罪<span class='krp-note'>刻/其</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='8362:8415'><span class='krp-note'>顙而涅之曰墨刑疑則赦從罰六兩曰鍰鍰黄鐵也閱實其罪/使與罰各相當辟婢亦反鍰徐戸關反六兩也鄭及爾雅同說</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='8415:8468'><span class='krp-note'>文云六鋝也鋝十一銖二十五分銖之十三也馬同又云賈逵/說俗儒以鋝重六兩周官劒重九鋝俗儒近是閱音恱顙素黨</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='8468:8496'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-11a' );" name="012-11a" class="pb">[012-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='8496:8531'><span class='krp-note'>反涅乃/結反</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>閱實其罪五/連見下文四</span>劓辟疑赦其罰惟倍閱實</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='8531:8560'>其罪<span class='krp-note'>截鼻曰劓刑倍/百爲二百鍰</span>剕辟疑赦其罰倍差閱實其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='8560:8610'>罪<span class='krp-note'>刖足曰剕倍差謂倍之又半爲五百鍰剕扶謂反倍差測/加反傳云五百鍰也馬云倍二百爲四百差者又加四百</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='8610:8649'><span class='krp-note'>之三分之一凡五百三十三鍰三分/鍰之一也刖音月又五罰反絶也</span>宫辟疑赦其罰六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='8649:8689'>百鍰閱實其罪<span class='krp-note'>宫淫刑也男子割勢婦人幽閉次死/之刑序五刑先輕轉至重者事之冝</span>大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='8689:8722'>辟疑赦其罰千鍰閱實其罪<span class='krp-note'>死刑也五刑疑各入罰/不降相因古之制也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='8722:8742'>墨罰之屬千劓罰之屬千剕罰之屬五百宫罰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='8742:8762'>之屬三百大辟之罰其屬二百五刑之屬三千</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='8762:8800'><span class='krp-note'>别言罰屬合言刑屬明刑罰同/屬互見其義以相備見賢遍反</span>上下比罪無僭亂辭勿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='8800:8839'>用不行<span class='krp-note'>上下比方其罪無聽僭亂之辭以/自疑勿用折獄不可行僭子念反</span>惟察惟法其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='8839:8867'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-11b' );" name="012-11b" class="pb">[012-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='8867:8908'>審克之<span class='krp-note'>惟當清察罪人之辭刑/以法理其當詳審能之</span>上刑適輕下服<span class='krp-note'>重刑有/可以虧</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='8908:8943'><span class='krp-note'>减則之輕/服下罪</span>下刑適重上服輕重諸罰有權<span class='krp-note'>一人有二/罪則之重</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='8943:8979'><span class='krp-note'>而輕并數輕重諸刑罰各有/權冝并必政反數色住反</span>刑罰丗輕丗重惟齊非齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='8979:9024'>有倫有要<span class='krp-note'>言刑罰隨丗輕重也刑新國用輕典刑亂國用/重典刑平國用中典凡刑所以齊非齊各有倫</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='9024:9065'><span class='krp-note'>理有/要義</span>罰懲非死人極于病<span class='krp-note'>刑罰所以懲過非殺人欲使/惡人極於病苦莫敢犯者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='9065:9098'>非佞折獄惟良折獄罔非在中<span class='krp-note'>非口才可以斷獄惟/平良可以斷獄無不</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='9098:9139'><span class='krp-note'>在中/正</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>罔非在中君陳爾/惟勿宥惟厥中</span>察辭于差非從惟從<span class='krp-note'>察囚/辭其</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='9139:9171'><span class='krp-note'>難在於差錯非從其/爲辭惟從其本情</span>哀敬折獄明啓刑書胥占咸庶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='9171:9218'>中正<span class='krp-note'>當憐下人之犯法敬斷獄之害人明開刑書相與占/之使刑當其罪皆庶幾必得中正之道當丁浪反</span>其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='9218:9258'>刑其罰其審克之<span class='krp-note'>其所刑其所罰其當詳/審能行之無失中正</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>其審克/之四上</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='9258:9286'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-12a' );" name="012-12a" class="pb">[012-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='9286:9331'><span class='krp-note'>文/二</span>獄成而孚輸而孚<span class='krp-note'>斷獄成辭而信當輸汝信於王謂上/其鞠劾文辭上時掌反下注同鞠九</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='9331:9372'><span class='krp-note'>六反劾亥代反/玉篇胡得反</span>其刑上備有并兩刑<span class='krp-note'>其斷刑文書上王/府皆當備具有并</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='9372:9403'><span class='krp-note'>兩刑亦/具上之</span>王曰嗚呼敬之哉官伯族姓朕言多懼<span class='krp-note'>敬/之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='9403:9453'><span class='krp-note'>哉告使敬刑官長諸侯族同族姓異/姓也我言多可戒懼以儆之儆音景</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>敬之哉二前/見康王之誥</span>朕敬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='9453:9483'>于刑有德惟刑<span class='krp-note'>我敬於刑當使/有德者惟典刑</span>今天相民作配在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='9483:9526'>下明清于單辭<span class='krp-note'>今天治民人君爲配天在下當承天意聽/訟當清審單辭單辭特難聽故言之相如</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='9526:9562'><span class='krp-note'>字馬悉亮反助/也治直吏反</span>民之亂罔不中聽獄之兩辭<span class='krp-note'>民之所/以治由</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='9562:9600'><span class='krp-note'>典獄之無不以中正聽獄之兩辭/兩辭棄虚從實刑獄清則民治</span>無或私家于獄之兩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='9600:9633'>辭<span class='krp-note'>典獄無敢有受貨聽詐/成私家於獄之兩辭</span>獄貨非寳惟府辜功報以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='9633:9668'>庶尤<span class='krp-note'>受獄貨非家寳也惟聚罪/之事其報則以衆人見罪</span>永畏惟罰非天不中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='9668:9696'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '012-12b' );" name="012-12b" class="pb">[012-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='9696:9736'>惟人在命<span class='krp-note'>當長畏懼惟爲天所罰非天道不中/惟人在教命使不中不中則天罰之</span>天罰不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='9736:9770'>極庶民罔有令政在于天下<span class='krp-note'>天道罰不中令衆民無/有善政在於天下由人</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='9770:9800'><span class='krp-note'>主不中將亦罰/之令力呈反</span>王曰嗚呼嗣孫今往何監非德于民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='9800:9840'>之中尚明聽之哉<span class='krp-note'>嗣孫諸侯嗣丗子孫非一丗自今巳/往當何監視非當立德於民爲之中</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='9840:9871'><span class='krp-note'>正乎庶幾明聽/我言而行之哉</span>哲人惟刑無疆之辭屬于五極咸中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='9871:9918'>有慶<span class='krp-note'>言智人惟用刑乃有無窮之善辭名聞於後丗以其/折獄屬五常之中正皆中有善所以然也屬音燭</span>受</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='9918:9957'>王嘉師監于兹祥刑<span class='krp-note'>有邦有土受王之善衆而治之者/視於此善刑欲其勤而法之爲無</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='9957:9965'><span class='krp-note'>疆之/辭</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='9965:9983'>監本纂圖重言重意互註尚書卷第十二</span><br/>
</p>
